# Space Miner

- Unity 6 mobile game (Android/iOS). Project root: `game/`.
- First-party assets live under `Assets/_Project/`. Third-party imports go in `Assets/ThirdParty/`.
- Scripts: `Core` (bootstrap/managers), `Gameplay`, `UI`, `Services` (save, ads, analytics).
- Prefer ScriptableObjects in `Data/` for tuning. Avoid the legacy `Resources/` folder.
- Documentation belongs in `docs/`, not inside Unity Assets.
